extensionDescription.message: Add-on that uses the cloudFile API to upload to FEX.net

mngFexIntro.message: !HTML! This extension provides Filelink support for Free FEX.net, an anonymous 100GB files upload service where links expire after 7 days.

mngProjectSupport.message: !HTML! To participate in the development of this extension or to report an issue, please visit the project issues page.
